values:
When jim and i make promises, we don't mean to keep them.   But our joint journal will soon be up and ready to amaze you

On a high note, I went to cake this weekend.  if you werent there then you missed out, it was a riot.  aden came home with one less shoe than he left home with, meaning he returned with three.  thanks to elliot for all the help on getting us home safely..  

Halloween party tonight which should be spectacular, we will update with further details on that tomorrow evening.  don't count on that, its been weeks since my last update.    but if you wanna come and you know ryan b than give me a call, i've been forbidden from putting any more numbers up on this page since the "disaster", more commonly known as the masterpiece of my creating of jimmys party.
jim and i are making a shared journal so look forward to that, it will be indescribable

we had a jukebox reuninon at jacobs yesterday, it was great.  kyle mika laura sage and luke and me went out to dinner and then to jakes to meet up with the rest of the gang. it was awesome, to say the least.
i have girl font, it means im good with the ladies

miss mikaline made this for me, let me tell you about her.  she is short, she is small, she is wonderful

thats enough about her, lets get talking about me.   I like to boast about my supriority, i am better than anyone on this earth  except for my mom, but only because she makes a mac and cheese dish worthy of the gods.
